&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;Seed Health is a microbiome science company pioneering clinically validated innovations for gut and whole-body health.&lt;strong&gt; &lt;/strong&gt;Our portfolio of gut-directed products is developed in collaboration with leading scientists and backed by human clinical research. We’re best known for DS-01® Daily Synbiotic—the #1 digestive health probiotic in the U.S.—trusted by millions of people for its benefits in and beyond the gut, including skin, immune, and heart health.&lt;/p&gt;
